In a small mixing bowl, mix cream cheese with basil pesto until smooth and creamy. Stir in olives and sliced pepperoncini. Open hoagie roll and evenly spread both insides with cream cheese mixture. Place artichoke heart slices over cream cheese. Place on top half of roll, layer Genoa, turkey and ham. Place on bottom half of roll, radicchio and tomato slice. Carefully place top onto bottom half of roll and press gently. Secure with long toothpicks, cut in half. Place on a plate and garnish with a whole pepperoncini and radicchio leaves (optional).